headline: Incyte’s Q2 2025 Earnings: What to Expect
summary: Incyte is gearing up to report its fiscal second-quarter earnings later this month, with analysts forecasting a sharp surge in profitability, projecting triple-digit year-over-year profit growth.

headline: Incyte to Report Second Quarter Financial Results
summary: WILMINGTON, Del., July 10, 2025--Incyte (Nasdaq:INCY) announced today that it has scheduled its second quarter financial results conference call and webcast for 8:00 a.m. ET on Tuesday, July 29, 2025.
